[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]

Tempulli and KEK (Kosova Electricity Corporation) sign memorandum of understanding.

2020

Tempulli sign cooperation agreement with the Faculty of Sports Sciences (FEFS) of the Public University of Prishtina “Hasan Prishtina”.

2020

Tempulli is accredited for training programs for operators of lift trucks, crane operators, and professional trainings for taxi and van drivers.

2020

Tempulli is a co-organizer of the 1st Edition of the International Short Films Festival “LIFE SAFETY”.

2019

Tempulli has been licensed to provide Driving Instructors education.

2019

Tempulli sign cooperation agreement with Faculty of Management Science and Informatics of the University of Žilina from Slovakia.

2018

Tempulli becomes an International Road Federation (IRF) member with equal rights.

2018

Tempulli gets additional international accreditation from IRU Academy for CPC periodic training on freight carriers.

2017

Tempulli sign cooperation agreement with Technical University of Berlin, respectively with the Institute of Land and Sea Transport Systems.

2017

Cooperation agreement is signed between Tempulli and the Technical University of Dresden.

2016

Tempulli signed Cooperation Agreement with University “Aleksandër Moisiu” Durrës.

2016

Tempulli signed Cooperation Agreement with University Sapienza of Rome; Faculty of Technical Sciences from UKLO University St. Kliment Ohridski; italian company "Politecnica".

2015

Tempulli becomes part of SEED Project which aims to harmonize professional qualifications of drivers in the region of Eastern Europe, including Kosovo, Serbia, Macedonia, BH and Croatia. Also, Tempulli signed Cooperation Agreement with European Road Stars Academy from Belgium on professional development programs.

2014

Tempulli is renamed again College and reaches agreements with MEST and other ministries, national and international institutions to organize national “Road safety” campaign. Tempulli starts the weekly TV show on “Road safety”.

2013

Tempulli celebrates its 20th anniversary. In the spring of this year Tempulli is accredited by MI to organize trainings for exams of managers and manipulators of dangerous goods (ADR), trainings for managers and professional drivers for national and international drivers for good and travelers (CPC).

2012

Tempulli is accredited internationally by International Roads Union – IRU Academy from Switzerland and it’s a full rights member.

2011

Tempulli is beneficiary of the joint Project of European Commission Tempus and is accredited by The Chartered Institute of Logistics and Transportation (CILT), UK.

2010

Tempulli based on recommendations of British Council for Accreditations from University College is converted on High Professional School accredited by KAA and licensed by MEST.

2009

Tempulli signs some collaboration agreements with national and international institutions on university studies area.

2008

Tempulli is authorized by Ministry of Transportation and Post-Telecommunications for professional training of vehicles technical controllers.

2007

Tempulli starts organization of the professional training for driving instructors.

2006

Tempulli marks new results especially on collaboration with local institutions especially on organizing the tutorials as per students needs.

2005

Tempulli establishes the High School and it is licensed by MEST for all traffic directions.

2004

Tempulli offers professional services to RTK to realize “Green Light” show as part of educational program.

2002

Tempulli organizes university studies on traffic and transportation and gets the preliminary accreditation from Department of Education, Science and Technology of UNMIK.

2001

Tempulli is one of the initiators for the establishment of Independent Union of Auto School of Kosovo and the Headquarter of this Union for Prishtina Region.

1997

Tempulli publishes the first number of “auto tempulli” magazine.

1996

Tempulli starts qualification of candidates for drivers.

1995

Tempulli starts organizing foreign language courses for all levels.

1994

Tempulli was established as a private and independent subject and through it Bureau has worked with analysis and expertise on traffic accidents.

1992
